        {
            "text": "The types of cancers in these studies included esophageal cancer, non-small-cell lung cancer, colon cancer, hepatocellular carcinoma, breast cancer, human melanomas, and tongue cancer. ",
            "section": "study characteristics",
            "paragraph_rank": 6,
