        },
        {
            "text": "Discussion",
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "LSD1 consists of several domains, including an N-terminal SWIRM domain, a conserved motif shared by many chromatin regulatory complexes, an amine oxidase domain, and a C-terminal tower domain. ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 10,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "[22][23][24] It cooperates with the CoREST and CtBP24 corepressor complex and demethylates histone H3K4 and H3K9 through this interaction. ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 10,
            "section_rank": 9,
            "ref_spans": [
                {
                    "start": 0,
                    "end": 4,
                    "type": "bibr",
                    "ref_id": "b22",
                    "text": "[22]"
                },
                {
                    "start": 4,
                    "end": 8,
                    "type": "bibr",
                    "ref_id": "b23",
                    "text": "[23]"
                },
                {
                    "start": 8,
                    "end": 12,
                    "type": "bibr",
                    "ref_id": "b24",
                    "text": "[24]"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "text": "25,26 Epigenetic changes in LSD1 have been shown to play a key role in carcinogenesis. ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 10,
            "section_rank": 9,
            "ref_spans": [
                {
                    "start": 0,
                    "end": 3,
                    "type": "bibr",
                    "ref_id": "b25",
                    "text": "25,"
                },
                {
                    "start": 3,
                    "end": 5,
                    "type": "bibr",
                    "ref_id": "b26",
                    "text": "26"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "text": "27 LSD1 can prevent the accumulation of the    dimethyl groups of p53, repressing p53-mediated transcriptional upregulation, preventing apoptosis, and contributing to human carcinogenesis via a chromatin modification mechanism. ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 10,
            "section_rank": 9,
            "ref_spans": [
                {
                    "start": 0,
                    "end": 2,
                    "type": "bibr",
                    "ref_id": "b27",
                    "text": "27"
                }
            ]
        },
        {
            "text": "Recently, many studies have been carried out to identify the prognostic role of LSD1 in various cancers. ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 10,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "However, insignificant or opposite results were also observed in some studies. ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 10,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "Since the prognostic value of LSD1 for tumor patients remains controversial, a meta-analysis was needed to explore the issue clearly.",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 10,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "To the best of our knowledge, this is the first meta-analysis focused on the association between LSD1 expression and patient survival. ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 11,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "The present study pooled the survival data of 1,149 cancer patients from nine studies and found that LSD1 overexpression was associated with poor OS in cancer patients (HR =1.80, 95% CI: 1.39-2.34, P=0.000). ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 11,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "The subgroup analyses grouped by ethnicity, cancer type, and HR estimate were consistent with the overall analysis. ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 11,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "It may suggest that detected LSD1 expression could be a prognostic factor in cancers.",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 11,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "Our meta-analysis also has several limitations that should be acknowledged. ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 12,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "First, only one study focused on Caucasian patients, which made it difficult to draw a firm conclusion on the prognostic value of LSD1 for Caucasian patients. ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 12,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "Second, the number of prognostic studies dealing with each type of cancer was relatively small, which might weaken the reliability of our results. ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 12,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "Moreover, well-designed clinical studies with a large number of cases for each specific cancer should be performed in the future to validate the relationship between LSD1 expression level and prognosis of patients with cancer. ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 12,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "Third, although the method for detecting LSD1 level in all included studies was immunohistochemistry, it was difficult to follow entirely consistent monitoring standards for the dyeing process, antibody concentration, and cutoff value of different tissues. ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 12,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "Fourth, we extracted data from survival curves because not all survival data of the enrolled studies were presented directly. ",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 12,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "These calculated HRs with their 95% CIs might be less reliable than the directly given data.",
            "section": "Discussion",
            "paragraph_rank": 12,
            "section_rank": 9
        },
        {
            "text": "Conclusion",
            "section_rank": 10
        },
        {
            "text": "The present meta-analysis indicated that increased LSD1 level was significantly associated with poor OS. ",
            "section": "Conclusion",
            "paragraph_rank": 13,
            "section_rank": 10
        },
        {
            "text": "More multicenter clinical investigations with larger sample sizes should be conducted to confirm these findings.",
            "section": "Conclusion",
            "paragraph_rank": 13,
            "section_rank": 10
        },
